Label: Description
Value: Database of Global Landslide Catalog from NASA collected from 1970 - 2019. It was generated using news feeds and is mostly capturing rain-induced landslide events. More information on metadata and original update source here: https://catalog.data.gov/dataset/global-landslide-catalog-export
